      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="fb5bc-102">使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding>对象将控件绑定到数据源时, 可以<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataSourceUpdateMode>使用枚举来指定对数据源进行更新的时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fb5bc-102">When a control is bound to a data source using a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> object, you can specify when an update to the data source will occur using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataSourceUpdateMode> enumeration.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="fb5bc-103">当更新模式为 "从不" 时, 可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.WriteValue%2A>方法强制更新数据源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fb5bc-103">When the update mode is Never, you can force the data source to be updated by using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.WriteValue%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="fb5bc-104">即使更新模式设置为 "从不", 在首次创建绑定时, 数据源也会更新, 因此至少会出现一次更新。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fb5bc-104">Even when the update mode is set to Never, the data source will be updated when the binding is first created, so at that least one update will always occur.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
